00:00:26.312 --> 00:00:28.026
but essentially it's an egg cooked inside

00:00:28.026 --> 00:00:29.233
this slice of bread.

00:00:29.233 --> 00:00:30.670
So the key component to this,

00:00:30.670 --> 00:00:32.883
I've heard some people complain that

00:00:32.883 --> 00:00:34.066
