'cause it's so simple.

00:00:36.313 --> 00:00:39.193
It's a piece of bread and an egg,

00:00:39.193 --> 00:00:40.589
but I think the reason is

00:00:40.589 --> 00:00:42.679
is just understanding,

00:00:42.679 --> 00:00:44.633
well, you have to have a big enough hole.

00:00:44.633 --> 00:00:45.840
That's what it really comes down to.

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:47.954
So you can use a biscuit cutter,

00:00:47.954 --> 00:00:49.579
